---
title: Middle Eastern Chicken & Garlic Rice with Cucumber Salsa & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Seasoning is everything, like a fairy Godmother it can transform any dish into a five-star standout. Tonight, it’s a Middle Eastern
seasoning that's lending its unique talents to the chicken. Magic is in the air!
